<br>
Just wanted to let everyone know about this @#%$. Let me give ya a brief run down of what happened:<br>
<br>
33 of us gathered for a Naggy raid, (Arocus) included. Raid was going fine, and Naggy was taken down. All of a sudden, son of a bitch..<br>
AROCUS has looted Cloak of the Flames<br>
AROCUS has looted Orb of Tashan<br>
AROCUS has looted Red Dragon Scales<br>
AROCUS has looted Hierophant's Crook<br>
AROCUS has looted Gold Plated Koshigatana<br>
<br>
AROCUS is not online...<br>
<br>
After Arocus looted ALL the items, he logged out in true ninja fashion, what a dumb ass. Anyway the GM's had to come LOG ON his character and give the items back to the RL. What was also funny is the GM was kind enough to provide the name of his main, Sidburn, perhaps some of you know him? <br>
<br>
Watch out for this guy, everyone should do their part in ignoring these 2 by not selling @#%$ to them, not grouping with them, and hopfully we can drive another bad egg off this server.<br>
<br>
If you want more info on the story just ask some of Avatar E., they hosted the raid along with HotU, they will provide info, and some have this logged. <br>
<br>
Sidburn, your done on EQ bro so might as well pack it up, thought what you did was pretty f*ckin sneeky eh? yeah we'll see where that gets ya, learn how the raid function works<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Peace<br>
